data.text: S√∏ren Aabye Kierkegaard (5 May 1813 ‚Äì 11 November 1855) was a Danish philosopher, theologian, poet, social critic and religious author who is widely considered to be the first existentialist philosopher. He wrote critical texts on organized religion, Christendom, morality, ethics, psychology, and the philosophy of religion, displaying a fondness for metaphor, irony and parables. Much of his philosophical work deals with the issues of how one lives as a "single individual", giving priority to concrete human reality over abstract thinking and highlighting the importance of personal choice and commitment. He was against literary critics who defined idealist intellectuals and philosophers of his time, and thought that Swedenborg, Hegel, Goethe, Fichte, Schelling, Schlegel and Hans Christian Andersen were all "understood" far too quickly by "scholars". Kierkegaard's theological work focuses on Christian ethics, the institution of the Church, the differences between purely objective proofs of Christianity, the infinite qualitative distinction between man and God, and the individual's subjective relationship to the God-Man Jesus the Christ, which came through faith. Much of his work deals with Christian love. He was extremely critical of the practice of Christianity as a state religion, primarily that of the Church of Denmark. His psychological work explored the emotions and feelings of individuals when faced with life choices.

[Tim Dekorasi Natal KMK 2016]
Pertama kali jadi kadiv yg kerjaaanya harus berkali" ketemu dan kerja bareng langsung sama anak" divisinya
Dari awal udh pesimis banget sama diri sendiri yg gabiasa mimpin, dan selalu berpikir gaakan sampe target bahkan udh berpikiran mau kerja rodi sendirian selama liburan, trus gmn paniknya tiap mau gawe ngesiapin bahan" dan gmn takutnya kalo udh ngundang anak" eh malah ngebuat mereka gabut
Ternyata segala keresahan itu makin lama makin menghilang semakin sering aku ketemu anak"
Walaupun dari 20an org yg diterima di dekor, yg dateng gawe ga pernah full team, tapi hari ini akhirnya kerjaan divisi kita selesai jugaa
Rencanaku buat kerja rodi sendirian pun gajadi dilaksanakan karena semua kita kerjain bareng bareng
Seneng banget udh dibolehin jadi kadiv dan ketemu sama anak-anak dekor ini, mulai dari kerja bareng, nyemen bareng, ngelakuin hal bodoh dan ngakak ngakak gajelas, bikin 274 lembar snowflake berbagai ukuran sampe denger kata snowflake aja udh najis banget rasanya, kadang juga kesannya kyk dibully sama anak divisi sendiri, trus pernah juga dikasihanin sama anak divisi sendiri gara" progress awal kita yg sangat lambat lol
Makasih buat kabid pensuasanaan yg kerjanya ga cuma ngawas dan ngamatin progress, yg udah ikut kerja bareng dekor dan selalu jadi tempat curhat soal dekor, emang acun kabid terbaik bangsa :) wkwk
Makasih juga pastinyaa buat anak anak dekorr yang udah daftar dekor, kerja bareng dan bingung bareng bareeng wkwk Ini sekumpulan anak anak yg bikin gawe divisi dekor tahun ini selalu penuh canda tawa 
Gawe kita udah selesai gais, hari minggu tanggal 22 nanti bakal jadi hari terakhir kita kerja bareng bareng sebagai dekor natal, semoga apa yang udah kita buat selama ini bisa menghiasi ruangan dengan baik di hari h nanti
Kita liat apakah pohon natal yg snowflakenya sudah dibuat stengah mati itu bakal sukses atau ga wkwkwkwk
